00:30:15.932 --> 00:30:19.392
quality of life any more than those patients who were getting the

491
00:30:19.412 --> 00:30:22.372
placebo for which the cancer was continuing to grow.

492
00:30:23.832 --> 00:30:26.472
So you look at this and say, for six

493
00:30:27.552 --> 00:30:31.472
added weeks of survival at this level of toxicity, can

494
00:30:31.512 --> 00:30:34.132
we do better? Our patients certainly deserve

495
00:30:34.172 --> 00:30:38.008
that.So this was a very patient-centric

