00:31:13.608 --> 00:31:15.828
level was in that personalized approach.

506
00:31:16.408 --> 00:31:20.288
And what the authors reported was significant improvement

507
00:31:20.368 --> 00:31:21.558
in overall toxicity,

508
00:31:23.128 --> 00:31:26.808
improvement in quality of life, while not compromising

509
00:31:26.888 --> 00:31:29.187
survival outcomes for these patients.

510
00:31:29.828 --> 00:31:33.717
So again, incorporating the patient experience into the real-world

511
00:31:33.808 --> 00:31:37.548
practice has helped to improve the day-to-day management

512
00:31:37.648 --> 00:31:40.488
of this drug in patients with colorectal cancer.

513
00:31:41.928 --> 00:31:45.568
Lonserf with bevacizumab also received an FDA

514
00:31:45.588 --> 00:31:46.188
approval

515
00:31:47.588 --> 00:31:51.188
within the past five years for, again, a marginal

516
00:31:51.248 --> 00:31:54.688
