00:32:45.188 --> 00:32:48.088
But the bevacizumab is given every two weeks.

531
00:32:48.888 --> 00:32:49.128
So

532
00:32:50.288 --> 00:32:54.048
simply by adjusting when the second week of the

533
00:32:54.088 --> 00:32:57.548
Lonserf is given to align it with the dosing of the

