920
00:55:56.866 --> 00:56:00.556
This is what the multimedia interactive patient education situation looked like.

921
00:56:01.086 --> 00:56:04.806
We videotaped it ourselves. We created

922
00:56:05.026 --> 00:56:08.146
vignettes of patients, real patients, and their parents,

923
00:56:08.806 --> 00:56:12.446
all ages, sexes, cultural, racial, ethnic

924
00:56:12.526 --> 00:56:15.946
backgrounds, different SES, in English and

925
00:56:15.986 --> 00:56:19.806
Spanish. And the viewer, the study participant, would

926
00:56:19.906 --> 00:56:23.726
choose which patient they identified with the most

927
00:56:24.206 --> 00:56:28.006
and watch that piece in the clinic. The video lasted 20 minutes.

928
00:56:29.346 --> 00:56:33.266
So each patient-parent dyad was introduced by the host,

929
00:56:33.946 --> 00:56:36.266
and these are the situations here. You can see them.

