00:56:50.526 --> 00:56:53.106
starving actor. We filmed it in Los Angeles.

934
00:56:54.286 --> 00:56:58.246
He described the benefits of 6-MP, how to overcome

935
00:56:58.306 --> 00:57:02.206
the challenges, what the physician and the nurse practitioner

936
00:57:02.246 --> 00:57:05.846
here are telling the patients about what happens if you don't take the 6-MP.

937
00:57:06.726 --> 00:57:07.886
We had an animation.

938
00:57:09.506 --> 00:57:11.986
Different for the younger kids, different for the older kids.

939
00:57:12.266 --> 00:57:14.476
This is the older kids, more grunge here.

940
00:57:15.186 --> 00:57:19.166
So the 6-MP tablets, the blasts are running after

941
00:57:19.206 --> 00:57:22.766
those white cells and accidentally swallow a

942
00:57:22.986 --> 00:57:26.486
6-MP tablet. Here, they're eating it, and then they implode.

