00:57:50.106 --> 00:57:52.866
and then that would be repeated daily.

951
00:57:53.546 --> 00:57:56.726
So this is what the web-based medication scheduling looked like.

952
00:57:57.606 --> 00:58:00.126
It was a secure, HIPAA-compliant

953
00:58:01.086 --> 00:58:05.046
application. The MD created that 6-MP schedule in

954
00:58:05.086 --> 00:58:08.966
the clinic, where it is how many tablets you need to take, what

