969
00:59:00.046 --> 00:59:03.146
It did much better in the older patients,

970
00:59:04.506 --> 00:59:07.736
where overall, there was a 4% improvement,

971
00:59:08.266 --> 00:59:12.005
but amongst those who were baseline non-adherers, there was a

972
00:59:12.066 --> 00:59:13.306
nine and a half percent

973
00:59:14.426 --> 00:59:18.046
